<div class="story"><p>Croatan Shores is a waterfront to waterfront community fronting the Atlantic Ocean to the east and Kitty Hawk Bay to the west. Situated in Kill Devil Hills and stretching from Indian Dr., just north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/first-flight-village.asp" title="First Flight Village">First Flight Village</a>, all the way to Clamshell Dr. in <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/sea-holly-ridge.asp" title="Sea Holly Ridge">Sea Holly Ridge</a>, Croatan Shores is one of the larger subdivisions on the beach with almost 1,000 properties. At the opposite ends of 3rd Street you will find a water access to Kitty Hawk Bay and a beach access to the Atlantic Ocean, both with parking. </p>
</div>